answerText: Omoo[10] Omoo and the aforementioned Typee are both novels by this author, whose other works include The Encantadas and White Jacket.

question: Question: Marie-Joseph-Paul-Yves-Roch-Gilbert du Motier, marquis de Lafayette [10] Identify this adventure novel, sometimes paired with a work subtitled "A Peep at Polynesian Life."
